	Content-Type : application/json
	Accept : application/json

NOTE :  
	* URL for Incident : https://api.vistara.io/api/v2/tenants/{clientId}/incidents/{incidentId}/notes/{noteId}
	* URL for Service Request : https://api.vistara.io/api/v2/tenants/{clientId}/serviceRequests/{serviceReqId}/notes/{noteId}

